Posting of applicable regulations

11(1)Repealed: [1983, c.8, s.11](/en/nb/laws/astat/snb-1983-c-8/latest/snb-1983-c-8.html)

11(2)An employer shall post and keep posted in a conspicuous place in the employers establishment a copy of all applicable minimum wage regulations.

11(3)Additional notice of any regulation made under [section9](#sec9_smooth) shall be given by employers to employees in such manner as the Lieutenant-Governor in Council may by regulation direct.

