Collective agreement in force after July16, 1976

23Where any class of employers or employees is covered by a collective agreement that became effective after July16, 1976 and provides for a minimum of eight paid holidays, including New Brunswick Day, that class of employers and employees are exempt from the application of [sections 18](#sec18_smooth) to [21](#sec21_smooth).

